<td>Hephaestus, forger of magic,<br />
descend upon this the body of thy priest and servant,<br />
lend us the strength of your arms.<br />
Prometheus, shape of man,<br />
descend upon this the body of thy priest and servant,<br />
lend us your fire and foresight.<br />
Morpheus, weaver of dreams,<br />
descend upon this the body of thy priest and servant,<br />
lend us your subtlety and vision.<br />
</td>
