Lend us your wheel of making.<br />
Hecate, caster of spells,<br />
Descend upon this the body of thy priestess and servant.<br />
Lend us the power of your magic.<br />
Aphrodite, goddess of love,<br />
Descend upon this the body of thy priestess and servant.<br />
Grant us eros, philos, aristos, agape.</td>
