<td width="40"><strong>P:</strong></td>
<td>I am the god, ever desiring.<br />
I am the stag in the woods,<br />
I am the sun in the noonday sky,<br />
I am the lover in the dark.<br />
I offer passion, strength, devotion and the swiftness of the hunt.</td>
